{"tid":1087800,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"世一江旻憓支持區","createTime":"2019-04-01T14:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T17:53:56.000Z","uid":36601,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d456cc4bc9de4738f7ef17d3c759f582df5dd07","tid":1087800,"uid":36601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:48:18.000Z","msg":"江旻憓（英語：Kong Man Wai, Vivian，1994年2月8日－），香港女子擊劍（銳劍）運動員。<br />\n<br />\n2019年1月，江旻憓在擊劍世界盃古巴站決賽擊敗法國劍手奧麗安&middot;馬洛（Auriane Mallo）奪得金牌。<br />\n<br />\n2月，江旻憓在擊劍世界盃巴塞隆拿站決賽擊敗韓國劍手李慧仁，贏得個人第二個世界盃冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n3月，江旻憓以較佳大賽成績壓過韓國的康映美，世界排名升至第一位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZvfaAVb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvfaAVb.jpg&h=0e587533&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Je4nr1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJe4nr1T.jpg&h=dafb3cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGOobtz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGOobtz.jpg&h=92b3165c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uJ0dGV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uJ0dGV.jpg&h=696205c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「香港傑出運動員」（2018年）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2POnEF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2POnEF.jpg&h=0f35488a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2d0dMm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2d0dMm.jpg&h=cf5c64ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8bd764123de6befe95969a7cacde06d9c18d17a","tid":1087800,"uid":143372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我會繼續努力"},{"pid":"3b5471f539bb2c43b0d602d7901f41e4e98ca4fd","tid":1087800,"uid":5883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d8bd764123de6befe95969a7cacde